<DATE_TIME> 1998-07-13 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Starting Line-ups for Brazil, France </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SAINT-DENIS, France, July 12 (Xinhua) -- Following the starting
line-ups for Brazil and France for the World Cup finals here on
Sunday:
</P>
<P>
Brazil: Taffarel, Cafu, Junior Baiano, Aldair, Roberto Carlos,
Dunga, Cesar Sampaio, Leonardo, Rivaldo, Ronaldo, Bebeto
</P>
<P>
France: Fabien Barthez, Bixente Lizarazu, Marcel Dasailly, Lilian
Thuram, Frank Leboeuf, Youri Djorkaeff, Didier Deschamps, Zinedine
Zidane, Emmanuel Petit, Christian Karembeu, Stephane Guivarc'h
</P>
</TEXT>
