maintaining peace and stability on the neighboring Korean
Peninsula.
</P>
<P>
He noted that China is fully prepared to work with the
government of the Republic of Korea (ROK) to establish a friendly
and cooperative bilateral relationship oriented to the next
century.
</P>
<P>
Jiang made the remarks during a meeting with ROK Foreign and
Trade Minister Park Chung-soo, who arrived in Beijing last
Saturday on a four-day visit to China.
</P>
<P>
