The ROK fully appreciate the fact that China successfully
hosted the recent visit by U.S. President Bill Clinton, said Park,
adding that the visit not only served the best interests of China
and United States, but the whole of Asia as well.
</P>
<P>
Park expressed hope for even greater progress in friendly and
cooperative ROK-China ties in the next century. 
