Cyprus would participate in the system through the Israeli MED1
Submarine Cable Ltd. company, which has undertaken the cable's
construction, operation and maintenance, the CYTA said.
</P>
<P>
The agreement is considered as one of the steps that Cyprus
takes to reinforce its role as a regional telecommunications hub.
