7.31 points to 421.31, the all-share Emas Index shrank 2.36 points
to 106.30, the Industrial Index fell 12.15 points to 854.64 and
the Second Board Index dropped 1.89 points to 93.07.
</P>
<P>
Losers led gainers by 515 to 100 while 107 counters were
unchanged, 201 untraded and 40 suspended.
</P>
<P>
The day's turnover stood at 128.754 million shares valued at
263.666 million ringgit (62.185 million U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
