million shares traded on the main board, industrial products
11.297 million shares, construction 8.578 million shares,
trading/services 39.067 million shares, infrastructure 1.227
million shares, finance 31.036 million shares, hotels 481,000
shares, properties 15.202 million shares, plantation 4.341 million
shares, mining 278,400 shares, trusts 83,000 shares, closed/fund
43,000 shares and loans 7.747 million shares. 
