<TEXT>
<P>
GENEVA, July 12 (Xinhua) -- Germany collected a total of 137
points to top the World Cup rowing overall final standings after
the third and final regatta of the world cup Rowing tournament in
Lucerne, Switzerland on Sunday.
</P>
<P>
Britain finished second with 112 points and Denmark came third
with 93 points followed by Australia in 86 and Romainia in 77.
</P>
<P>
